  <shortDescription><![CDATA[<p>Explore two or three famous resorts in awe-inspiring settings linked by one of the most spectacular rail journeys across the Alps. Start your stay in the infamous resort of <a data-udi="umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2735e2389f7c411cb3061226ce7548d1}" title="Chamonix">Chamonix</a>, moving on to <a data-udi="umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722" href="/{localLink:umb://document/2e09d5bd5fae466db4b3c37d49150722}" title="Zermatt">Zermatt</a>, via the picturesque Mont Blanc Express railway journey. For an extended stay, continue on to <a data-udi="umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/0fe9200934b24cd49d20e1cea080f5da}" title="Grindelwald">Grindelwald</a> in the Bernese Oberland.</p>]]></shortDescription>
